'''Pandor's Hydrospanner''' was a chain of repair and maintenance shops. They sold equipment for [[Starship/Legends|starships]] and [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]], among other items. Most Pandor's Hydrospanner shops also traded in smaller starships. One of their most popular shops was situated in [[Sector Alpha]] on [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']]. They also had a [[Pandor's Hydrospanner (Ord Mynock)|store on Ord Mynock]].

